Mission.Author: Forboding Angel
Mission.Description:
In this mission, your Objective is to destroy the enemy, Overseer Sigcourt, before he can escape. There have been reports of reinforcements called in to escort Overseer Sigcourt to safety, but it is unknown the size and number of these escorts. It is rumored that he will be making his escape to the east.
Do not let him get away, Overseer!
Mission.Name: Evolution RTS - Destroy Overseer Hablon

TriggerLogic.Name: GUI Message
TriggerLogic.Message:
In this mission, your Objective is to destroy the enemy, Overseer Sigcourt, before he can escape. There have been reports of reinforcements called in to escort Overseer Sigcourt to safety, but it is unknown the size and number of these escorts. It is rumored that he will be making his escape to the east.
Do not let him get away, Overseer!
Overseer Sigcourt is making good his escape! You must destroy him before he can get away!
Oversight is very displeased, Overseer! The council has convened and demands your presence. You had better have an excellent reason for letting Overseer Sigcourt slip through your grasp!

Excellent work, Overseer! The council will be pleased! Overseer Sigcourt possesed vital information concerning our operations in New Iammas. If that information had made it into the wrong hands, our war effort would have taken a heavy blow.
Go have a drink, Overseer! You've earned it!
